name: Saizeriya
description: Saizeriya is a global chain Italian Casual Dining Restaurant.  We, Saizeriya, are well known in Italian food culture as the Italian cuisine is recognized for quality and healthy food.  We, Saizeriya, want to provide most affordable, quality, and healthy Italian Food Dining Experience to our customers around the world.  We have more than over 1300 outlets worldwide. Located mainly in Japan, Singapore, Taiwan, Shanghai, Beijing, Guangzhou, and Hong Kong, (7 regions). Currently, there are 16 outlets in Singapore. We are targeting to open 50 outlets by year 2020 for our valued customers convenience sake.
